# AVD-DS-0002: Dockerfile.frontend serves via nginx on port 80, which requires a
# privileged port bind; nginx's own master process drops to an unprivileged user
# for worker processes. Switching the whole container to non-root would require
# rebasing to nginx-unprivileged or remapping to a high port — tracked separately,
# not part of the base Dockerfile lint gate.
AVD-DS-0002
